BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:MHK7jxbTbs_w29DoFKXYK
SUMMARY:March Madness Watch Party at Five Iron Golf - Seattle Capitol Hill
DTSTAMP:20260314T140407Z
DTSTART:20260327T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Five Iron Golf is your College Basketball HQ this March! Gather
	 your crew and book 1–2 simulator bays for up to 12 people \\(6 people per
	 bay\\) for a bracket-busting watch party experience. Enjoy all-day TV cov
	erage of college basketball alongside cutting-edge golf and multisport sim
	ulators\, a locally-inspired menu\, and custom beverage packages.\n\nBook 
	your watch party for March 19 or 20 and you'll automatically be entered to
	 win a 20-person happy hour with drinks and appetizers — a $1\,000 value!\
	n\nGroup packages can include reserved event space\, team-specific décor\,
	 a dedicated staff member\, full-screen and/or picture-in-picture viewing\
	, a customizable menu\, beverage packages\, free club rentals\, multisport
	 simulators\, and table games. Select the "Small Event" option at booking 
	to ensure simulator bays are placed side-by-side. Availability of select f
	eatures varies by location.\n\nPromotions:\n\nHappy Hour – "It's 5i o'Cloc
	k Somewhere" \\(Monday–Friday\, 3–6 PM\\)\n\nEnjoy $5 bottomless boneless 
	wings\, $10 bottomless bone-in wings\, $5 select beers/cans/cocktails\, $5
	 dips \\(guacamole\, hot honey ricotta\, hummus\\)\, half-off pizzas\, and
	 $5 featured shots. Dine-in only at participating locations\; simulator re
	ntal may be required.\n\n5i After Dark – "Swing In\, For Less"  \\(Sunday–
	Thursday 9 PM to close | Friday–Saturday 10 PM to close\\)\n\nFeatures $29
	/hr simulator rentals plus the same great food and drink specials as Happy
	 Hour\, with wings priced per dozen rather than bottomless. Dine-in only a
	t participating locations\; simulator rental may be required.\n\nhttps://s
	eatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/march-madness-watch-party-at-five-iro
	n-golf-seattle-capitol-hill/18268907/2026-03-27T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Spor
	ts & Outdoors
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/march-madness-watch-party
	-at-five-iron-golf-seattle-capitol-hill/18268907/2026-03-27T00
LOCATION:Five Iron Golf - Seattle Capitol Hill\, 1525 11th Ave Suite 100\, 
	Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-sports
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT12H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:baC8E5TNKxphRB3cCMTwL
SUMMARY:Sturtevant's Ski-Ya-Later Sale: Up to 50% Off Ski and SnowboardGear
DTSTAMP:20260314T140407Z
DTSTART:20260327T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:PNW skiers and snowboarders—spring is the smartest time to upgr
	ade! Sturtevant's \\(part of Christy Sports\\) is hosting the annual Ski-Y
	a-Later Sale from March 6-29\, offering up to 50% off current-season skis\
	, snowboards\, boots\, bindings\, apparel\, and more—perfect as spring sto
	rms bring late-season conditions and families plan ahead during spring bre
	ak.\n\nShop in-person at our Bellevue locations for expert tuning & repair
	\, custom boot fitting\, water sports rentals\, and more: Sturtevant's – 1
	3131 NE 20th St.\, Bellevue\, WA 98005 \\(425.869.7669\\) Hours: Mon-Fri 1
	0 am-7 pm\, Sat-Sun 10 am- 6 pm\n\nSturtevant's Ski Mart – 13219 NE 20th S
	t.\, Bellevue\, WA 98005 \\(425.637.8958\\) Hours: Mon-Fri 10 am-7 pm\, Sa
	t-Sun 10 am-6 pm\n\nOr head to Tacoma: Sturtevant's Ski Mart – 2220 So. 37
	th St.\, Tacoma\, WA 98409 \\(253.473.1134\\) Hours: Mon-Fri 10 am-7 pm\, 
	Sat-Sun 10 am-6 pm.\n\nGreat for families: Stop by for kids' fit checks\, 
	season rental info\, and early purchases before fall pricing. All discount
	ed items are final sale\; selection varies by store. Also shop online at c
	hristysports.com or sturtevants.com. Upgrade your gear locally this spring
	—visit Sturtevant's Bellevue or Tacoma today.\n\nDates: March 6 – March 29
	\, 2026 \\(Progressive discounts: Up to 30% off March 6-12 with the best s
	election\; up to 40% off March 13-19\; up to 50% off March 20-29 for the d
	eepest savings\\)\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/sturtev
	ant-s-ski-ya-later-sale-up-to-50-off-ski-and-snowboardgear/18276036/2026-0
	3-27T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/sturtevant-s-ski-ya-later
	-sale-up-to-50-off-ski-and-snowboardgear/18276036/2026-03-27T00
LOCATION:Sturtevant's Ski Mart\, 13219 NE 20th St.\, Bellevue\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-sports
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT8H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:YShiaAi5CWIuzH2QZEgD6
SUMMARY:Pilates for Gardeners
DTSTAMP:20260314T140407Z
DTSTART:20260327T210000Z
DESCRIPTION:Taught by Jo Anne Iaciofano. Grab your mat\, kick off your shoe
	s\, and join this Pilates-inspired class to improve body movement\, core s
	trength\, and muscle control. This beginner’s friendly class\, using mind-
	body connection and breath\, will take you through a series of exercises w
	ith an emphasis on technique and fluidity. We will focus on those areas mo
	st stressed during gardening by using your core to power the muscles incre
	asing your energy and endurance. All levels are welcome. Wear comfortable 
	clothing and be prepared to workout barefoot. Please bring a yoga or Pilat
	es mat\, towel\, and water. This class will take place in the Aaron Educat
	ion Center.  $17.50 BBGS Member/$25 Non-Member.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcit
	y.com/events/#/details/pilates-for-gardeners/17923217/2026-03-27T00\n\nFro
	m SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/pilates-for-gardeners/179
	23217/2026-03-27T00
LOCATION:Bellevue Botanical Garden\, 12001 Main St\, Bellevue\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-sports
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
